它是一坯烂作。

1235
01:10:46,400 --> 01:10:51,020
I can't think of a literary masterpiece of the past 50 to 60 years.
我想不出过去五六十年间的文学巨作。

1236
01:10:51,560 --> 01:10:55,060
There are some very entertaining books, but
有一些非常有趣的书，但……

1237
01:10:55,060 --> 01:10:59,560
not of the stature and power of Homer, Dante, and Shakespeare.
不及荷马、但丁与莎士比的宏大与力量。

1238
01:11:00,160 --> 01:11:02,340
And the last question I have is,
还有我最后一个问题是，

1239
01:11:02,440 --> 01:11:06,840
does civilization make us less creative?
文明让我们更少创造吗？

1240
01:11:10,460 --> 01:11:13,440
Does being a civilization make us more creative?
成为文明让我们更有创造力吗？

1241
01:11:13,440 --> 01:11:16,420
Are we more ashamed of exploring,
我们更自豪于探索吗？

1242
01:11:16,740 --> 01:11:19,080
of being curious, of playing?
好奇的事，玩耍的事？

1243
01:11:20,100 --> 01:11:23,860
Are we less creative because of civilization?
文明让我们更少创造吗？

1244
01:11:25,660 --> 01:11:27,000
All right. Okay.
好的。好。

1245
01:11:27,100 --> 01:11:29,160
So that's it, guys. Any questions?
好了，大家。还有问题吗？

1246
01:11:38,120 --> 01:11:41,900
Okay. So next week,
好的。下周，

1247
01:11:41,940 --> 01:11:44,480
we will do the 11th edition of the Abyssic Caliphate.
我们将进行第十一版的深渊哈里发。

1248
01:11:44,540 --> 01:11:45,780
Okay? All right.
好的？好了。

1249
01:11:45,800 --> 01:11:49,580
So I will see you guys next Tuesday.
那我下周二见你们。
